quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  61,10,Yemwe abemeye! Mbarangire ubucuruzi buzabarokora ibihano bibabaza
  61,11,"Nimwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi), munaharanire inzira ya Allah mukoresheje imitungo yanyu namwe ubwanyu. Ibyo ni byo byiza kuri mwe, iyaba mwari mubizi"
  61,12,"(Nimubigenza mutyo, Allah) azabababarira ibyaha byanyu, anabinjize mu busitani butembamo imigezi, n’ubuturo bwiza mu busitani buhoraho (Ijuru). Uko ni ko gutsinda guhambaye"
  61,13,"(Azanabaha) n’ibindi mukunda: ugutabarwa guturutse kwa Allah n’intsinzi ya bugufi. Bityo, tanga inkuru nziza ku bemeramana"
  61,14,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimube abashyigikira (idini rya) Allah, nk’uko Issa mwene Mariyamu yabwiye abigishwa be ati “Ni ba nde banshyigikira mu nzira ya Allah?” Abigishwa baravuga bati “Turi abashyigikiye Allah.” Nuko itsinda rya bamwe muri bene Isiraheli riremera, irindi rirahakana. Maze dushyigikira abemeye batsinda abanzi babo"